==English==
===Etymology===
From [[belly]] + [[ache]]

===Noun===
'''bellyache'''
#Any [[pain]] in the [[belly]], [[stomach]], or [[abdomen]].
#:''Eating too much candy can give you a '''bellyache'''.''

===Intransitive verb===
'''bellyache'''
#To [[complain]] or [[whine]], especially needlessly.
#:''Quit '''bellyaching''' about the problem and help us fix it.''